+- Missing context (what info would have helped): No extra product context was needed for the review itself; the only missing execution detail was an in-repo fallback path for the required pipeline files, because the absolute pipeline directory is outside the writable sandbox.
+- Scope questions (anything you weren't sure if it's in scope): The task included conflicting execution-order instructions for the “very first action” marker file and the repo sync/reset step. I treated both as mandatory and kept the review scope limited to Fix 1–7 only.
