5. `P2` Fix 5: the cross-guest review button `Оценить блюда гостей` still renders in the table tab.
6. `P1` Fix 6: the guest fallback label still exposes the last 4 characters of the raw guest ID (`Гость 5331` pattern).
7. `P3` Fix 7: cancelled orders are still filtered only by raw `o.status !== 'cancelled'`, not by the stage-based `internal_code === 'cancel'` path.

